RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: select a.function_id from smtb_function_description a , smtb_menu b where a.Lang_Code = global.lang and a.function_id = b.function_id and ((b.type_string in ('M','ELM' ) and substr(a.function_id,3,1) not in ('S' ,'P') and a.main_menu||a.sub_menu_1||a.sub_menu_2 is not null))order by function_id
